sequenceDiagram
    participant Client
    participant UserService
    participant DynamoDB
    participant EventBridge
    participant NotificationService

    Client->>UserService: POST /v1/users
    UserService->>UserService: Extract email from Cognito JWT
    UserService->>DynamoDB: Save user
    UserService->>EventBridge: Publish user.created
    EventBridge-->>NotificationService: Async notification event
    UserService-->>Client: 201 Created